                fetch distribution file from site ----> fetch – Fetch files from remote nodes
                uncompress file ----------------------> unarchive – Unpacks an archive after (optionally) copying it from the local machine
                move it to installation path ---------> archive – Creates a compressed archive of one or more files or trees
                add go to system path ----------------> archive – Creates a compressed archive of one or more files or trees ??
            
